      "description": "This E46 M3 is a superlative example of the marque, featuring the high-revving S54 inline-six engine equipped with individual throttle bodies and Double VANOS variable valve timing. The powertrain delivers seamless torque through a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission to a factory limited-slip differential. This chassis has undergone proactive subframe reinforcement and a documented rod bearing replacement to ensure long-term structural and mechanical integrity. The suspension geometry remains true to factory specifications with fresh bushings and dampers, providing the precise turn-in and feedback expected of a flagship M-car. Every body panel retains its original VIN tag and factory-applied finish, evidencing a life of climate-controlled preservation. A turn-key acquisition for the discerning collector.",
